  "instructions": [
    "Grind black mustard seeds in a mortar and pestle until coarse.",
    "Heat ghee or neutral oil in a medium saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add red bell pepper to the saucepan and cook until slightly softened.",
    "Add brown rice and cook for 1-2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add 2 cups of water to the saucepan and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Fluff pilaf with a fork and season with salt to taste.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley before serving."
  ],
